# Example .tape file for VHS
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600

Type "go run . --origin 'go.sum database tree'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 4s
Type "l"
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3s
Left
Left
Sleep 2s
Type "g"
Sleep 200ms
Type "22"
Sleep 2s
Enter
Sleep 5s
Type "q"
Sleep 200ms
